----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gcalendar URL 
(DO NOT clone see instruction 1.)
https://github.com/slgobinath/gcalendar

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. 
COPY gcalendar directory (/home/ian/gcalendar) from Raspberry Pi 4 at 192.168.68.8 
(use winscp to copy to /home/ian/ on remote server)

2.
TO Install gcalendar FROM /home/ian/gcalendar

RUN 
python3 setup.py install
OR
python3 install setup.py


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
